snippet.title: SportsBarVR - Preview Trailer | PS VR
snippet.description:
Preview trailer of SportsBarVR containing pre-release gameplay footage of a multiplayer hangout session  with Four (4) players interacting with each other and their environment as well as playing Pool, Air Hockey, Darts, and Skeeball.
